data.description: Beautiful & Spacious 4 Bedroom, 2 Full Bath on Corner Lot.  Freshly Painted and Brand NEW Carpet just Installed.  Main Level Entry with Open Concept, Living Room, Dining Room and Kitchen featuring Stainless Steal Appliances, Granite Countertops & Island make it the perfect place for Entertaining and Hosting Gatherings.  Slider off Dining Room leads to Deck and Vinyl Privacy Fenced in Yard . Upper Level with 3 Bedrooms, and Full Bath. Lower Level features a Family Room, access to the rear yard & 1 Car Garage and Full Bathroom. 4th Bedroom on lower level.  Move in Ready. Convenient to Shopping, Great location for commuting close to Routes - 100 & 97- 30 minutes to Fort Meade, Annapolis & Baltimore.
